1
00:00:08,708 --> 00:00:09,708
Shane.

2
00:00:09,791 --> 00:00:11,208
Shane... can you love me again?

3
00:00:11,375 --> 00:00:11,916
Shane...

4
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:13,000
Hear me out.

5
00:00:14,416 --> 00:00:15,916
I could say it a hundred

6
00:00:16,541 --> 00:00:17,541
or a thousand times...

7
00:00:18,750 --> 00:00:20,458
I really don't love you.

8
00:00:27,166 --> 00:00:29,291
Then what about everything we had?

9
00:00:31,250 --> 00:00:32,410
The time we spent together...

10
00:00:32,791 --> 00:00:34,000
Taking care of each other...

11
