12
00:00:38,250 --> 00:00:40,250
Because you were good to me.

13
00:00:41,541 --> 00:00:43,666
I didn't dare leave you.

14
00:00:45,166 --> 00:00:47,166
But it was just pity.

15
00:00:49,750 --> 00:00:51,416
It wasn't love.

16
00:00:56,791 --> 00:00:59,333
If you want me to say I love you,

17
00:01:01,333 --> 00:01:02,875
I'll say it for you.

18
00:01:09,833 --> 00:01:12,000
I can lie to make you feel better.

19
00:01:17,105 --> 00:01:19,564
But I can't lie to my own heart.

20
00:01:19,855 --> 00:01:21,314
You understand, right?

21
00:01:21,772 --> 00:01:22,980
Please tell me you do.

22
00:01:35,605 --> 00:01:36,845
Since things have come to this,

23
00:01:38,480 --> 00:01:39,564
I want to tell you that

24
00:01:41,897 --> 00:01:43,605
