32
00:02:09,397 --> 00:02:10,689
Even though we're not.

33
00:02:11,564 --> 00:02:14,189
It's just not right. It's not.

34
00:02:18,927 --> 00:02:21,177
Then why didn't you just tell me?

35
00:02:22,218 --> 00:02:23,260
Why?

36
00:02:25,427 --> 00:02:26,802
If I had told you,

37
00:02:29,718 --> 00:02:31,718
I was afraid of hurting you.

38
00:02:43,593 --> 00:02:44,593
Alright then.

39
00:02:45,927 --> 00:02:47,343
I'll say it right here.

40
00:02:49,885 --> 00:02:51,718
That I don't like you.

41
00:02:55,552 --> 00:02:57,427
I don't love you one bit.

42
00:02:58,052 --> 00:02:59,052
Understand?

43
00:02:59,510 --> 00:03:01,510
Stop. Stop talking.

44
00:03:02,093 --> 00:03:05,177
Enough. I don't want to hear it.

45
00:03:06,260 --> 00:03:07,260
I...

46
00:03:07,802 --> 00:03:09,218
I know I was stupid.

47
00:03:10,218 --> 00:03:11,510
For giving my heart away

48
00:03:12,468 --> 00:03:14,010
and letting myself

49
00:03:14,010 --> 00:03:16,468
fall for someone like you.

50
00:03:17,927 --> 00:03:20,927
I'm an idiot. I'm so stupid.

51
00:03:21,260 --> 00:03:22,093
I'm stupid.

52
00:03:22,260 --> 00:03:24,260
Such an idiot. So stupid.

53
00:03:24,385 --> 00:03:26,010
I'm the stupid one.

54
00:03:28,462 --> 00:03:29,587
I'm an idiot.

55
00:03:30,129 --> 00:03:32,171
I'm an idiot. I'm so stupid.

56
