Nat.

58
00:03:42,421 --> 00:03:43,671
Nat.

59
00:03:44,962 --> 00:03:46,046
Nat.

60
00:03:46,171 --> 00:03:47,171
I'm the stupid one.

61
00:03:48,212 --> 00:03:49,212
I'm an idiot.

62
00:03:49,712 --> 00:03:51,212
- Nat, wait.
- I'm the stupid one.

63
00:03:53,587 --> 00:03:55,046
I could say it a hundred

64
00:03:55,212 --> 00:03:56,004
