65
00:03:56,171 --> 00:03:57,879
I really don't love you.

66
00:03:59,004 --> 00:04:01,254
I'm an idiot.

67
00:04:01,796 --> 00:04:03,296
Nat.

68
00:04:07,129 --> 00:04:08,837
Nat. Nat.

69
00:04:21,254 --> 00:04:22,754
The necklace is a bit thin,

70
00:04:24,129 --> 00:04:25,254
but the design is sick.

71
00:04:26,337 --> 00:04:27,421
What now?

72
00:04:29,504 --> 00:04:31,171
A new scent to heal the heart...

73
00:04:31,879 --> 00:04:32,962
That's not bad at all.

74
00:04:34,171 --> 00:04:35,254
Plus, we can sell the clip.

75
00:04:35,712 --> 00:04:37,712
You really are a piece of shit.

76
00:04:41,692 --> 00:04:42,858
Nat.

77
00:04:48,817 --> 00:04:49,942
Nat. Nat. Hey...

78
00:04:50,525 --> 00:04:52,025
Nat. Nat.

79
00:04:52,192 --> 00:04:53,233
- Nat.
- Hey!

80
00:04:56,567 --> 00:04:57,858
