136
00:08:22,702 --> 00:08:25,285
Stop talking! You're bleeding out.

137
00:08:25,452 --> 00:08:26,452
Shane.

138
00:08:34,243 --> 00:08:35,785
I want this ring...

139
00:08:36,577 --> 00:08:37,618
