140
00:08:39,118 --> 00:08:40,410
In my place.

141
00:08:41,577 --> 00:08:42,577
Enough.

142
00:08:43,035 --> 00:08:44,910
You need to stop talking.

143
00:08:46,702 --> 00:08:48,452
Please don't die on me.

144
00:08:48,952 --> 00:08:50,202
Just stay with me.

145
00:08:51,035 --> 00:08:53,868
