149
00:09:11,956 --> 00:09:13,914
Even if it's a lie, it's fine.

150
00:09:15,789 --> 00:09:18,456
No. Just stay with me.

151
00:09:19,997 --> 00:09:22,664
Just stay with me. Please don't go.

152
